sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as 👤 Pengguna
    participant BR as 🖥️ Browser<br/>(chat.html)
    participant WS as 🔀 WS Proxy<br/>(ws_proxy.py)
    participant TCP as 🔒 TCP Server<br/>(server.py)
    participant DB as 🗄️ SQLite<br/>(stealthnet.db)

    Note over U,DB: ══════ FASE 1: KONEKSI & HANDSHAKE ══════

    U->>BR: Buka halaman login.html
    BR->>WS: WebSocket connect ws://host:8080
    WS->>TCP: TCP/TLS connect (port 5000)
    TCP-->>WS: TLS Handshake selesai ✓
    WS-->>BR: WebSocket connection established ✓

    Note over U,DB: ══════ FASE 2: REGISTRASI / LOGIN ══════

    U->>BR: Input username & password → klik Login

    BR->>WS: WebSocket frame JSON<br/>{"type":"REGISTER","username":"rei","password":"..."}
    Note over WS: Tambahkan 4-byte<br/>prefix header
    WS->>TCP: [0x00 0x00 0x00 0x28] + JSON payload

    TCP->>DB: SELECT username FROM users WHERE username=?
    DB-->>TCP: (null — user baru)
    TCP->>DB: INSERT INTO users (username, password) VALUES (?,?)
    DB-->>TCP: OK

    Note over TCP: Auto-login setelah<br/>registrasi berhasil

    TCP->>DB: UPDATE users SET status='online', last_seen=? WHERE username=?
    DB-->>TCP: OK

    Note over U,DB: ══════ FASE 3: PENGIRIMAN DATA AWAL ══════

    TCP->>WS: [prefix] {"type":"LOGIN_SUCCESS","message":"Welcome rei"}
    WS->>BR: WebSocket frame → LOGIN_SUCCESS

    TCP->>DB: SELECT user2 FROM friends WHERE user1=?
    DB-->>TCP: [ ] (daftar teman)
    TCP->>DB: SELECT room_name, invite_code, role FROM rooms JOIN room_members...
    DB-->>TCP: [ ] (daftar room)
    TCP->>DB: SELECT * FROM friend_requests WHERE receiver=? AND status='pending'
    DB-->>TCP: [ ] (permintaan teman)

    TCP->>WS: [prefix] {"type":"INITIAL_DATA","friends":{},"rooms":[],...}
    WS->>BR: WebSocket frame → INITIAL_DATA

    Note over U,DB: ══════ FASE 4: BROADCAST STATUS ONLINE ══════

    TCP->>DB: SELECT user1 FROM friends WHERE user2=? (ambil semua teman rei)
    DB-->>TCP: [daftar username teman]

    loop Untuk setiap teman yang sedang online
        TCP->>WS: [prefix] {"type":"ONLINE_STATUS","username":"rei","online":true}
        WS->>BR: Frame → ONLINE_STATUS<br/>(kirim ke browser teman rei)
    end

    BR-->>U: ✅ UI chat muncul<br/>Daftar teman & room ter-render<br/>Indikator online aktif (titik hijau)
